RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: TXTMS_RULE.RULE_CODE=TXTMS_SLAB.RULE_CODE AND TXTMS_RULE.EFFECTIVE_DATE=TXTMS_SLAB.EFFECTIVE_DATE AND TXTMS_RULE.EFF_END_DATE=TXTMS_SLAB.EFF_END_DATE AND TXTMS_RULE.COUNTRY=TXTMS_SLAB.COUNTRY AND TXTMS_RULE.CUSTOMER=TXTMS_SLAB.CUSTOMER AND TXTMS_RULE.CUST_TAX_GROUP=TXTMS_SLAB.CUST_TAX_GROUP AND TXTMS_RULE.CURRENCY = TXTMS_SLAB.CURRENCY AND TXTMS_RULE.NATIONALITY =TXTMS_SLAB. NATIONALITY

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT COUNTRY_CODE, DESCRIPTION FROM STTMS_COUNTRY WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION SELECT 'ALL','ALL COUNTRIES' FROM DUAL
SELECT CUST_GROUP,CUST_GROUP_DESC FROM OLTM_CUST_GROUP WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND CUST_GROUP_TYPE = 'T' UNION SELECT 'ALL' , 'ALL CUSTOMER GROUPS' FROM DUAL
SELECT CUSTOMER_NO, SHORT_NAME FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION SELECT 'ALL','ALL CUSTOMERS' FROM DUAL
SELECT CCY_CODE,CCY_NAME FROM CYTM_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' UNION SELECT '$$$' as CCY_CODE, '$$$' as CCY_NAME from DUAL
SELECT R.TAX_RULE FROM TXTM_TAX_RULE R ,TXTMS_TAX_GROUP G ,TXTMS_RULE T WHERE R.TAX_GROUP = T.RULE_CODE AND R.TAX_GROUP = G.TAX_GROUP AND G.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND G.RECORD_STAT = 'O'
SELECT COUNTRY_CODE, DESCRIPTION FROM STTMS_COUNTRY WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION SELECT 'ALL','ALL COUNTRIES' FROM DUAL
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION SELECT '*.*','ALL CURRENCIES' FROM DUAL
SELECT DISTINCT RULE_ID, DESCRIPTION FROM LFTB_ICCF_RLAVL WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RULE_TYPE = 'T'
